    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持众议院共和党政府融资计划，推迟债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/house-republicans-say-they-have-deal-on-funding-us-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普与众议院共和党人达成协议，避免美国政府关门，并暂停联邦债务上限两年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/house-republicans-say-they-have-deal-on-funding-us-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国新总理计划本周末任命新政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/french-premier-puts-macron-s-legacy-pension-reform-on-the-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理弗朗索瓦·贝鲁计划在周末组建新内阁，并在 2 月中旬之前提交预算，他警告称，如果不能解决当前的政治混乱，可能会给国家带来灾难性的后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/french-premier-puts-macron-s-legacy-pension-reform-on-the-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 19:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
